import React from "react";
import { Navigate, Route, Routes, Redirect } from "react-router-dom";
import Home from "./Home"
import Jobs from "./Jobs"
import Contact from "./Contact"
import JobEdit from "../JobForm/JobEdit"
import JobMenu from "../list/Menu";
import JobNew from "../JobForm/NewJob";

function Router(){
    return(
<Routes>
    <Route exact={true} path="/" to={<Navigate to="/home"/>}/>
    <Route exact={true} path="/home" to={<Home/>}>
      
    </Route>
    <Route exact={true} path="/jobs" to={<Home/>}>
      <JobMenu/>
    </Route>
    <Route path="/jobs/new" to={<Home/>}>
      <JobNew/>
    </Route>
    <Route  path="/jobs/:job_id/edit" to={<Home/>}>
      <JobEdit/>
    </Route>
    <Route exact={true} path="/contacts" to={<Home/>}>
      <Contact/>
    </Route>
</Routes>
    
)}

export default Router
